    <entry>
      <title>C++ Primer (2) 字符串，向量，函数(from chapter3、6)</title>
      <link href="/2022/03/04/cpp-primer-2/"/>
      <url>/2022/03/04/cpp-primer-2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="C-Primer-2-字符串，向量，函数-from-chapter3、6"><a href="#C-Primer-2-字符串，向量，函数-from-chapter3、6" class="headerlink" title="C++ Primer (2) 字符串，向量，函数(from chapter3、6)"></a>C++ Primer (2) 字符串，向量，函数(from chapter3、6)</h1><blockquote><h3 id="Chapter-3——字符串、向量和数组"><a href="#Chapter-3——字符串、向量和数组" class="headerlink" title="Chapter 3——字符串、向量和数组"></a>Chapter 3——字符串、向量和数组</h3></blockquote><h4 id="3-1-命名空间的using声明"><a href="#3-1-命名空间的using声明" class="headerlink" title="3.1 命名空间的using声明"></a>3.1 命名空间的using声明</h4><p>格式为<code>using namespace::name;</code></p><pre class="line-numbers language-cpp"><code class="language-cpp"><span class="token keyword">using</span> std<span class="token operator">::</span>cin<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//只调用std空间中中的cin</span><span class="token keyword">using</span> <span class="token keyword">namespace</span> std<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//调用std空间中的所有名字</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="3-2-标准库string"><a href="#3-2-标准库string" class="headerlink" title="3.2 标准库string"></a>3.2 标准库string</h4><ul><li><p>初始化<br><img src="//lee-abcde.github.io/2022/03/04/cpp-primer-2/String1.png" alt></p></li><li><p>cin读入：<code>cin&gt;&gt;s;</code>会忽略开头的空格，从第一个有效字符开始，到第一个空白结束。 </p></li><li><p>getline读入：<code>getline(cin,line)</code>会读入包括空格，直到读入换行符结束，但不读入换行符。<br><img src="//lee-abcde.github.io/2022/03/04/cpp-primer-2/String2.png" alt></p></li><li><p>String遍历</p><pre class="line-numbers language-cpp"><code class="language-cpp">string s<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">for</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">auto</span> c<span class="token operator">:</span> s<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//仅仅用来遍历</span><span class="token keyword">for</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">auto</span> <span class="token operator">&amp;</span>c<span class="token operator">:</span> s<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//遍历的同时可以改变s的值</span>s<span class="token punctuation">[</span>i<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 下标访问的关键是使用前要判断s是否为空，否则s[0]越界</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="3-3-标准库Vector"><a href="#3-3-标准库Vector" class="headerlink" title="3.3 标准库Vector"></a>3.3 标准库Vector</h4><p>vector是<strong>模板</strong>而不是类型，需要指定数据类型，如<code>vector&lt;int&gt; v</code>。vector可以容纳大多数的对象，但是引用不是对象，所以无法容纳引用。<br><img src="//lee-abcde.github.io/2022/03/04/cpp-primer-2/Vector1.png" alt>  </p><h4 id="3-4-迭代器"><a href="#3-4-迭代器" class="headerlink" title="3.4 迭代器"></a>3.4 迭代器</h4></li><li><p>迭代器使用<code>auto b=v.begin(),e=v.end();</code>当v为空，begin和end返回的迭代器是相同的。注意end()返回的迭代器指向的一个不存在末尾元素，仅仅作为标记。<br><img src="//lee-abcde.github.io/2022/03/04/cpp-primer-2/Iter1.png" alt><br>注意：不能解引用<strong>尾后迭代器和非法迭代器</strong></p></li><li><p><code>for(auto it=v.begin(); it!=v.end(); ++it)</code><br><img src="//lee-abcde.github.io/2022/03/04/cpp-primer-2/Iter2.png" alt> </p></li><li><p>迭代器类型</p><pre class="line-numbers language-cpp"><code class="language-cpp">vector<span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token keyword">int</span><span class="token operator">></span><span class="token operator">::</span>iterator it1<span class="token punctuation">;</span>string<span class="token operator">::</span>iterator it2<span class="token punctuation">;</span>vector<span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token keyword">int</span><span class="token operator">></span><span class="token operator">::</span>const_iterator it3<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//只能读元素不能写元素</span>string<span class="token operator">::</span>const_iterator it4<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//只能读元素不能写元素</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li><li><p><code>-&gt;</code>运算符，把解引用和访问成员结合在一起<code>it-&gt;mem</code>和<code>(*it).mem</code>是等价的。</p></li><li><p><strong>限制：1.不能在范围for循环内对vector添加元素 2.使用任何改变对象容量的操作，如<code>push_back</code>，可能会导致迭代器失效</strong> (注：范围for循环形如<code>for(int val:numbers)</code>)<br><img src="//lee-abcde.github.io/2022/03/04/cpp-primer-2/Iter3.png" alt> </p><blockquote><h3 id="Chapter-6——函数"><a href="#Chapter-6——函数" class="headerlink" title="Chapter 6——函数"></a>Chapter 6——函数</h3><p>建议把函数声明定义在头文件中，在源文件中定义。<br>如果函数无法改变形参的值，建议把其声明为常量引用。</p></blockquote></li><li><p>函数重载：函数名字相同但形参列表不相同（不允许两个函数只有返回值不相同，但形参列表相同；形参列表不区分顶层const，<code>int find(Phone*);</code>和<code>int find(Phone* const);</code>是相同的）</p></li><li><p>内联函数：将函数直接在调用点直接替换展开。是代码向编译器发出的请求，编译器可以直接忽略。</p></li><li><p>预处理宏：<code>assert(expr)</code>如果表达式为假则终止程序，否则什么也不做。<code>assert</code>定义在<code>cassert</code>头文件中。<br>注意：宏名字在程序内必须唯一，含有<code>cassert</code>头文件则不能使用<code>assert</code>当做变量名、函数或者实体。</p></li><li><p>NDEBUG预处理变量：NDEBUG宏是Standard C中定义的宏，专门用来控制assert()的行为。如果定义了这个宏，则assert不会起作用。</p><pre class="line-numbers language-cpp"><code class="language-cpp"><span class="token macro property">#<span class="token directive keyword">ifdef</span> NDEBUG</span><span class="token macro property">#<span class="token directive keyword">define</span> assert(x) ((void)0)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//如果定义了NDEBUG，就禁止assert使用</span><span class="token macro property">#<span class="token directive keyword">else</span></span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li><li><p>函数指针</p><pre class="line-numbers language-cpp"><code class="language-cpp"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//定义</span><span class="token keyword">bool</span> <span class="token function">lengthCompare</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">const</span> string <span class="token operator">&amp;</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token keyword">const</span> string <span class="token operator">&amp;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">bool</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">*</span>pf<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">const</span> string <span class="token operator">&amp;</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token keyword">const</span> string <span class="token operator">&amp;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//声明函数指针</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//赋值</span>pf<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token operator">&amp;</span>lengthCompare<span class="token punctuation">;</span>pf<span class="token operator">=</span>lengthCompare<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//两种赋值语句都是等价的</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//使用</span><span class="token keyword">bool</span> b1<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">pf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"AAA"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">"NNN"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">bool</span> b2<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">*</span>pf<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"AAA"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">"NNN"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>注意：重载函数的函数指针需要进一步明确的定义。此外还可以定义返回函数指针的函数。</p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
